@root=http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### User signin
POST {{root}}/auth/signin
content-type: application/json

{
    "phone": "0123456789",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### User signout
POST {{root}}/auth/signout
content-type: application/json

### Who am I?
GET {{root}}/auth/whoami
content-type: application/json